    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Produce social posts with Airtable and WordPress for your team\n\n**Pattern:** Content Generation · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nProduce social posts with Airtable and WordPress for your team. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual engagement is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nHourly Schedule → Required Fields Present? → Frame the Assignment → Coordinator Agent → Unpack Sections → Persist Deliverable to Airtable → Summarize Run Stats → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to content generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating engagement in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Google AI API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "6d1e917f-33fe-c327-a42b-560cdac3e83b",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
